<p>Drawers can come from any direction of the document. Use the following classes on drawers to determine the direction they should be exposed from.</p>

<ul class="list-disc pl-8">
	<li><code>.drawer--left</code></li>
	<li><code>.drawer--right</code></li>
	<li><code>.drawer--top</code></li>
	<li><code>.drawer--bottom</code></li>
</ul>

