Drawers are triggered by specifying the drawer ID in the <code>data-drawer</code> property.

{% highlight "html" %}
<!-- Drawer Trigger -->
<div class="p-2">
	<button class="js-drawer-trigger btn btn--outline" data-drawer="drawer-1">
        <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
    </button>
</div>
{% endhighlight %}

<p>Drawers should go near the closing body tag.</p>

